ARGUMENT

| Step | Hyp | Ref | Expression |

| 1 |  | #P_ominf4 | |- -. _om e. Fin4 |
| 2 |  | #P_reldom | |- Rel ~<_ |
| 3 | 2 | #P_brrelex2i | |- ( _om ~<_ A -> A e. _V ) |
| 4 |  | #P_isfin4 | |- ( A e. _V -> ( A e. Fin4 <-> -. E. x ( x C. A /\ x ~~ A ) ) ) |
| 5 | 3, 4 | #P_syl | |- ( _om ~<_ A -> ( A e. Fin4 <-> -. E. x ( x C. A /\ x ~~ A ) ) ) |
| 6 |  | #P_domfin4 | |- ( ( A e. Fin4 /\ _om ~<_ A ) -> _om e. Fin4 ) |
| 7 | 6 | #P_expcom | |- ( _om ~<_ A -> ( A e. Fin4 -> _om e. Fin4 ) ) |
| 8 | 5, 7 | #P_sylbird | |- ( _om ~<_ A -> ( -. E. x ( x C. A /\ x ~~ A ) -> _om e. Fin4 ) ) |
| 9 | 1, 8 | #P_mt3i | |- ( _om ~<_ A -> E. x ( x C. A /\ x ~~ A ) ) |
